name: Coinbase Tokenized Stock on Binance
public_notice: Coinbase Tokenized Stocks represents assets being traded on various Crypto Exchanges each with their own methodology. This does not directly represent the underlying asset to be traded on the Nasdaq Global Select Market.
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please contact hello@coingecko.com if you think this is an error

description.en:
Coinbase Tokenized Stocks represents assets being traded on various Crypto Exchanges each with their own methodology. This does not directly represent the underlying asset to be traded on the Nasdaq Global Select Market.


Coinbase anticipates that its Class A common stock will begin trading on the Nasdaq Global Select Market under the ticker symbol “COIN” on April 14, 2021.
